# Developer — docs

## Workflow

1. `gh issue view <N> --repo aharbii/movie-finder-docs`
2. Find `## Agent Briefing` — if missing, stop
3. Read only the files listed in the briefing
4. Create branch from `main`
5. Implement, validate locally with `make mkdocs` (from root)
6. Commit → PR in `aharbii/movie-finder-docs`

## Key tools

```bash
make mkdocs        # renders PlantUML PNGs + serves MkDocs at :8001
make structurizr   # Structurizr C4 at :18080
```

Discover current PlantUML files:
```bash
ls docs/architecture/plantuml/
```

## Patterns

- ADR template: `docs/architecture/decisions/index.md`
- New diagram: follow `NN-description.puml` naming, add render reference in MkDocs nav
- Never generate `.mdj` files — PlantUML only

## After PR merges

```bash
git add docs
git commit -m "chore(docs): bump to latest main"
```
